iplinary work to modify and update models and\nparameterisations initially developed for specific planetary atmospheres to\nmake them more broadly applicable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 May 2005 09:03:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2005 08:01:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
